MENU
Thank you for flying with American Airlines. Today's menu selections
are inspired by acclaimed restaurateur, Sam Choy. Along with our
partners, intervine and bobby stuckey, master sommener and
restaurateur, we have carefully selected wines to complement the
menu. Our wine list includes fine wines from around the world, and
has received top recognitions in the 2018 Global Traveler Wines on the
Wing awards and Business Traveler Cellars in the Sky 2017 awards. On
behalf of today's flight crew and our more than 100,000 employees
worldwide, we wish you a pleasant journey.
